FeedEntry, Serializable, Cloneable, Map<Object,Object>
public class FedoraObjectProxy
extends Properties
implements FeedEntry

This class is a basic, basic container for a Fedora object. We'll be interested primarily in the Properties, but we'll want to implement the FeedEntry methods.
